commentPostTextItems.html: Sri Lanka have won by 131 runs and make a pretty picture
Ashraful says " 357 was too large a target to be chased down " and " bowlers did not bowl well". He is hopeful that they can do well in the matches to come
Sangakkara is the Man of match and says "It's nothing new to open as I have played pretty much from 1 to 9"
Jayawardene  is happy to have got things right in the first match and is happy that youngsters have performed
Thanks for following our coverage and it's good night from all of us here
